/knee-and-ankle-support'),(188,'Silicone Range','silicone-range','','','','',53,'en',1,'hospital-apparel-linen-and-personal-protection/health-personal-care/silicone-range'),(189,'C-Cure','c-cure','','c-cure ','c-cure, health','c-cure, health',54,'en',1,'hospital-apparel-linen-and-personal-protection/health-personal-care/c-cure'),(190,'STERILIZATION, ANTISEPTICS & DISINFECTANTS','sterilization-antiseptics-disinfectants','<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 2.5rem;\">Sterilization, Antiseptics &amp; Disinfectants</h1>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">An antiseptic is an antimicrobial substance which can be applied to living tissue to reduce the possibility of infection. a disinfectant is a substance which is used on a non-living object to destroy microorganisms. Sterilization is the process of destroying microorganisms. There are no degrees of sterilization - an object is either sterile or non-sterile. Sterilization is extremely important in places like a hospital, where doctors and surgeons use instruments for surgical procedures. Sterilization products have been the backbone of healthcare delivery since the discovery of their role in reduction of infection. The usage of antiseptic surgical methods was championed by Joseph Lister. The sterilization procedure uses either one of heat, radiation or chemicals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Types of Sterilization, Antiseptics and Disinfectants products</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">Sterilization products, antiseptics, and disinfectants are used while doing invasive tests, surgical procedures, cleaning of instruments, equipment and premises, cleaning of hospital linen, cleaning surfaces, killing microbes present on hands etc. They come in various forms and chemical compositions based on the application.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">1.Hand Sanitizer</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">A hand sanitizer provides rapid disinfection from a broad spectrum of microbes present on skin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">2.Surgical Prep Solution and Antiseptics</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These are antiseptic agents to reduce microbes present at the incision site prior to incision. These can contain alcohol, povidine iodine, triclosan and chlorhexidine.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">3.Instrument and Equipment Detergents and Disinfectants</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These Detergents and Disinfectants are utilized to disinfect equipment and instruments. They can be composed of Glutaraldehyde, Propanol, OPA, and preoteolytic enzymes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.Linen Disinfectant</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">Linen Disinfectant are used to disinfect used hospital linen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">5.Surgical Scrub/ Hand Wash</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These products are used by operating team prior to intraoperative procedures for eliminating transient flora and inhibiting growth of microbes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">6.Surface &amp; Environment Disinfectant</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These are utilized to routine clean surfaces in health care set ups and have a broad spectrum activity against bacteria and eliminate other microbes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">7.Sterilization Trays</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These trays are designed to protect instruments during sterilization and storage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">8.Sterilization Indicators &amp; Tapes</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">The sterilization indicators and tapes are used for reliable monitoring and tagging during various sterilization procedures.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">9.Sterilization Packaging</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These are high strength medical grade paper with plastic polypropylene backing.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">10.Fogger Machine</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">These machines are used in hospitals for fumigation in place of fumigators and are highly effective for sanitation purpose.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Buy Sterilization, Antiseptics &amp; Disinfectants products on Smart Medical Buyer</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #788188; font-family: \'Work Sans\', sans-serif;\">Smart Medical Buyer has sterilization products from the following companies - 3M Healthcare,Schuelke,Torrel, Zenith Chemicals &amp; Polchem Hygiene Labs. Popular brands like Microshield, Avagard, Desmanol, Steridex, Tridex, etc. are available at attractive prices. We provide the widest range of brands with an easy ordering process and door step delivery.</p>','','','',55,'en',1,'sterilization-antiseptics-disinfectants');
