ault Shipping Settings and customize it fit to your fulfillment Model. Our Buyers expect their purchases to be well packed and to arrive on time . The Default Lead Time to ship / Fulfillment legacy is 2-3 Business Days .</li>\r\n<li>Octroi Charges if any will be borne by the seller /Vendor .</li>\r\n<li>The Orders that are not shipped and Confirmed as Shipped within 72 Hours of the last shipping date will be cancelled.</li>\r\n<li>2.5% of order Value will be charged as cancellation charges if the order is cancelled by the seller for any reason other then the buyer requested cancellation or if the order is auto cancelled by the zepomart as explained above .</li>\r\n<li>If your want to create a &ldquo;buy one and Get One &rdquo;promotion for two products , It is necessary to create a live listing for both Products .</li>\r\n<li>If an order is in Open / Pending State for More than 3 days , You should contact Seller/ Vendor Support .</li>\r\n<li>It is not advisable to include any marketing or promotional material with packing material.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>CUSTOMER SERVICE</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You should respond to the buyer quires within 24 Hours to maintain Good performance on customer Contact response time .</li>\r\n<li>If buyer provide a negative feedback , You can eighter resolve the issue by contacting the buyer through zepomart &ldquo;Customer Message Centre&rdquo;and request removal of the feedback , or post a response to the negative feedback on the website .</li>\r\n<li>Buy can Claim A-Z guarantee if a seller fail to deliver the product within</li>\r\n<li>3 days from the date of Maximum estimated delivery date , If the buyer receive the defective , Damaged or not the item depicted in the description, or if the buyer does not receive the refund or replacement as per policy .</li>\r\n<li>You should respond A-Z Claim Notification from &ldquo; zepomart&rdquo; within 7 calendar days</li>\r\n<li>You are required to take return or provide refund up-to 7Days from the date of delivery in accordance with &ldquo; zepomart&rdquo; Refund and return policy .</li>\r\n<li>Generally , zepomart.com pays the proceeds of your sales to your bank account 14 days after you register with our vendor Panel . Subsequently , the settlement process repeats every 7 days.</li>\r\n<li>If you don&rsquo;t meet your performance target you will receive a warning notifications by the &ldquo;Vendor&rsquo;s Performance Team&rdquo; to improve your performance on priority. Your account may get suspended immediately, If you miss your performance target by a large margin. You will get 90 days time for improving the performance to avoid suspension.</li>\r\n<li>It is prohibited to bribe buyers for positive feedback .</li>\r\n<li>It is prohibited to use buyer information for online and offline marketing purpose .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Communications</h3>\r\n<p>When you use the Platform or send emails, other data, information, or communication to us, you agree and understand that you are communicating with us through electronic records and you consent to receive communications via electronic records from us periodically or as and when required. We may communicate with you by email or any other mode of communication, electronic or otherwise.</p>\r\n<h3>Zepomart Platform for Transaction and Communication</h3>\r\n<p>The Platform is a platform that users utilize to independently meet and interact with one another for their transactions. Zepomart is not and cannot be a party to any transaction or dispute between users on the Platform.</p>\r\n<h3>Consequently:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>All commercial/contractual terms are offered by you and agreed upon between you and buyers alone. The commercial/contractual terms include (without limitation) price, shipping costs, payment methods and terms, date, period, and mode of delivery, and warranties and after-sales services related to products and services. Zepomart does not determine, advice, have any control, or in any way involve itsel